=== SOLAR_COLLECTOR ===
# id: 14
# title: The Solar Collector
# chinese_title: 集光器
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

An automated solar collection array still functions on the station's sunward side. Its panels track the distant star with mechanical precision, charging capacitor banks that no one has drained in years. The stored energy is immense.

* [Drain some energy to your equipment]
  ~ gain_radical("日")
  "日" (rì) — sun, day
* [Reroute power to life support]
  ~ heal(15)
  "电" (diàn) — electricity, power
* [Overload a capacitor as a weapon charge]
  ~ gain_item("emp_grenade")
  "雷" (léi) — thunder, lightning
